e at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that returns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":", then add a computed shape source to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the computed shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNComputedShapeSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","url":"